reviewText: Women and babies are dying because hospitals and doctors can't profit if they accept that less is more in the majority of deliveries.
I attribute my four natural births to the information and inspiration in this documentary! A fascinating eye opener! Totally empowering!
This documentary changed my world.  It's a must see.
While I love this documentary, the actual DVD was not burned properly. It will not play in a DVD player. It only works in my laptop :(
